headline: The Bull Case For CVS Health (CVS) Could Change Following Raised Earnings Guidance and Key Segment Strength
summary: CVS Health recently reported a robust third quarter, surpassing analyst expectations with a significant increase in adjusted earnings per share and raising full-year 2025 guidance, driven by strong performance in key segments and successful integration of acquired Rite Aid and Bartell Drugs prescription files. These developments reflect CVS Health's renewed operational momentum under new leadership, as the company sharpens its focus on more profitable growth areas and leverages its expanded...
